import { Nav } from "react-bootstrap";
const NavBar = () => {
  return (
    <Nav
      className="justify-content-center bg-dark text-light sticky-top"
      defaultActiveKey="/"
      as="ul"
    >
      <Nav.Item as="li">
        <Nav.Link href="/">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faEarthAmericas} /> {} Home
        </Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
      <Nav.Item as="li">
        <Nav.Link eventKey="link-1">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faRocket} />
          {} Space Crafts
        </Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
      <Nav.Item as="li">
        <Nav.Link eventKey="link-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faMeteor} />
          {} Planets
        </Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
    </Nav>
  );
};

export default NavBar;
